paragraphs.text:
%md
# UV와 오존전량 상관분석
## description
### ETL
#### Extract
- 데이터 항목: 기후변화 감시자료 중 자외선, 오존전량(성층권오존)
- 출처: 기상자료개방포털 (자외선: [link](https://data.kma.go.kr/data/gaw/selectUVRaysRltmList.do?pgmNo=631), 오존전량: [link](https://data.kma.go.kr/data/gaw/selectOzoneRltmList.do?pgmNo=630))
- 측정일: 2017년
- 지점: 안면도
- 형태: csv

#### Transform
1. spark context기반 csv read (euc-kr 인코딩 적용)
2. 컬럼명 영문으로 초기화
3. Uv와 ozone 데이터프레임 station_code, date 를 key로 하여 join
4. string형으로 되어있는 값들 double형으로 일괄변환 (udf_floatize)
5. 결측치 제거 (dropna)

#### Load
- sql 인터프리터로 plotting
- parquet로 저장 가능
-

%md
# 2017 UV - Ozone

%pyspark

uv = spark.read\
          .option('header', 'true')\
          .option('encoding', 'euc-kr')\
          .csv('file:///home/witlab/uv_ozone/2017_anmyeon_uv.csv')
uv.show()
cols_uv = ['station_code', 'date', 'sum_uva', 'max_uvb']

uv = uv.toDF(*cols_uv)
uv.show()

%pyspark

oz = spark.read\
          .option('header', 'true')\
          .option('encoding', 'euc-kr')\
          .csv('file:///home/witlab/uv_ozone/2017_anmyeon_ozone.csv')
oz.show()
cols_oz = ['station_code', 'date', 'avg_ozone']

oz = oz.toDF(*cols_oz)
oz.show()

oz.wr

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_floatize

uvoz = uv.join(oz, ['station_code', 'date'])
uvoz.show()

uvoz_r = uvoz.withColumn('sum_uva', udf_floatize('sum_uva'))\
             .withColumn('max_uvb', udf_floatize('max_uvb'))\
             .withColumn('avg_ozone', udf_floatize('avg_ozone'))\
             .dropna()

uvoz_r.show()
uvoz_r.printSchema()
uvoz_r.createOrReplaceTempView('uvoz')

%md
# 2013 ~ 2017 UV - Ozone

%pyspark

uv = spark.read\
          .option('header', 'true')\
          .option('encoding', 'euc-kr')\
          .csv('file:///home/witlab/uv_ozone/2013-2017_anmyeon_uv.csv')
uv.show()
cols_uv = ['station_code', 'date', 'sum_uva', 'max_uvb']

uv = uv.toDF(*cols_uv)
uv.show()

%pyspark

oz = spark.read\
          .option('header', 'true')\
          .option('encoding', 'euc-kr')\
          .csv('file:///home/witlab/uv_ozone/2013-2017_anmyeon_ozone.csv')
oz.show()
cols_oz = ['station_code', 'date', 'avg_ozone']

oz = oz.toDF(*cols_oz)
oz.show()

%pyspark

ae = spark.read\
          .option('header', 'true')\
          .option('encoding', 'euc-kr')\
          .csv('file:///home/witlab/uv_ozone/2013-2017_anmyeon_aerosol.csv')
ae.show()
cols_ae = ['station_code', 'date', 'avg_aerosol']

ae = ae.toDF(*cols_ae)
ae.show()

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_floatize

uvoz = uv.join(oz, ['station_code', 'date'])
uvoz.show()

uvoz_r = uvoz.withColumn('sum_uva', udf_floatize('sum_uva'))\
             .withColumn('max_uvb', udf_floatize('max_uvb'))\
             .withColumn('avg_ozone', udf_floatize('avg_ozone'))\
             .dropna()

uvoz_r.show()
uvoz_r.printSchema()
uvoz_r.createOrReplaceTempView('uvoz')

%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_floatize

uvozae = uv.join(oz, ['station_code', 'date'])\
           .join(ae, ['station_code', 'date'])
uvozae.show()

uvozae_r = uvozae.withColumn('sum_uva', udf_floatize('sum_uva'))\
                 .withColumn('max_uvb', udf_floatize('max_uvb'))\
                 .withColumn('avg_ozone', udf_floatize('avg_ozone'))\
                 .withColumn('avg_aerosol', udf_floatize('avg_aerosol'))\
                 .dropna()

uvozae_r.show()
uvozae_r.printSchema()
uvozae_r.createOrReplaceTempView('uvozae')

%pyspark

print(uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']].describe())
print(uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']].corr())

%pyspark

import pandas as pd
from statsmodels.stats.outliers_influence import variance_inflation_factor

# pdf_sample = uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']]
pdf_sample = uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']]

vif = pd.DataFrame()
vif["VIF Factor"] = [variance_inflation_factor(pdf_sample.values, i) for i in range(pdf_sample.shape[1])]
vif["features"] = pdf_sample.columns
vif

%pyspark
import statsmodels.formula.api as smf
import statsmodels.api as sm

pdf_test = uvozae_r.toPandas()[['max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']]

multi_linear = smf.ols(formula='max_uvb ~ avg_ozone + avg_aerosol', data=pdf_test).fit()
print(multi_linear.summary())

%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_date2yday

uvozae_rd = uvozae_r.withColumn('yday', udf_date2yday('date'))
uvozae_rd.show()

%pyspark

print(uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']].describe())
print(uvozae_r.toPandas()[['sum_uva', 'max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol']].corr())

%pyspark
import statsmodels.formula.api as smf
import statsmodels.api as sm

pdf_test = uvozae_rd.toPandas()[['max_uvb', 'avg_ozone', 'avg_aerosol', 'yday']]

multi_linear = smf.ols(formula='max_uvb ~ avg_ozone + avg_aerosol + yday', data=pdf_test).fit()
print(multi_linear.summary())
